These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, rock, soul
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, epic, action, drama
House: farmhouse, craftsman, townhouse, gothic-revival
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is between the person watching epic movies and the fan of folk##2
3. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | rock      | indie      | soul    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | satire | epic | action |
| House     | craftsman    | gothic-revival       | townhouse     | farmhouse     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, blues, country, ambient
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, police-officer, scientist, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, thriller
1. the police-officer is on the far left##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the scientist##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the fan of blues##1
7. the fan of country is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre          | trance     | ambient     | blues       | country    |
| Job         | police-officer | scientist   | pilot | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | superhero | romance    | epic        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia, tulip, daisy
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, trance, salsa
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1
8. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Flower      | begonia | dahlia  | tulip    | daisy |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop    | salsa | d&b | trance  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, dutch, colombian, french
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, folk, house, funk
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is between the fan of folk and the italian##2
2. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the colombian is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the french##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the french is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
8. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality          | colombian   | italian     | dutch | french |
| Music-Genre   | house | funk | d&b   | folk     |
| Pet           | turtle | lizard      | goat     | dog       |

