.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
City: london, prague, marseilles, san-francisco
House: tower, farmhouse, futuristic, cottage
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance, western
1. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
3. the futuristic house is the person watching action movies##1
4. the tower house is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to prague##2
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
8. the person traveling to marseilles is the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| City          | marseilles      | san-francisco | prague      | london |
| House           | farmhouse | tower | cottage | futuristic   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | western   | drama     | action   |

