.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, oliveros, vegafina, baccarat
City: san-francisco, rome, hannover, miami
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Cigar           | dannemann    | oliveros   | vegafina | baccarat |
| City   | san-francisco     | hannover   | miami         | rome        |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | golf         | rowing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, tulip, sunflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
City: boston, hamburg, edinburgh, liverpool
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person who growstulip is the person who growstulip##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Flower         | tulip    | dahlia  | amaryllis | sunflower   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| City   | liverpool      | edinburgh | hamburg | boston  |

