.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, tea, 7up
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy, rose, begonia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage          | tea | iced-tea    | 7up | sprite    |
| Flower         | rose     | begonia | daisy  | iris |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

