.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, rock, ambient
4 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, rabbit, frog
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea            | water     | fanta      |
| Music-Genre           | dubstep    | ambient | rock     | hip-hop |
| Pet   | goat | rabbit    | mouse | frog    |

