.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, bird, dog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, june, november
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Pet          | rat   | bird | rabbit | dog |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| Birthday   | december | march   | june    | november   |

