.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, mexican, american, chinese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, drama, scientific
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, october, may
1. the mexican is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the chinese##3
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the american is on the right of the indian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality           | chinese | mexican        | indian   | american  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy             | animation     | scientific | drama  |
| Birthday         | august           | may | november   | october |

