.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, soul, electronic, rock
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, project-manager, teacher, writer
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, traveling, writing
1. the writer is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the fan of country is on the left or right of the teacher##3
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the fan of soul##2
7. the fan of country is the project-manager##1
8. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre    | country   | electronic   | soul    | rock |
| Job         | project-manager | teacher    | nurse      | writer |
| Hobby   | cooking      | writing | traveling | hiking   |

