.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, house, soul
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, swisher, cain
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the fan of classical is between the person drinking coffee and the fan of soul##2
3. the fan of r&b is the cain-smoker##1
4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the fan of house##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
8. the fan of house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the swisher-smoker is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | coffee      | almond-milk | milk       | iced-tea  |
| Music-Genre       | house | classical | soul    | r&b |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | siglo         | swisher | cain     |

