.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-14::.
House: modern, wooden, ranch-style, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, folk, disco, punk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, time-travel
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the ranch-style house is the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
6. the modern house is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the wooden house is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| House          | townhouse          | ranch-style     | modern   | wooden   |
| Music-Genre           | punk | techno | folk | disco |
| Movie-Genre   | animation          | time-travel | romance   | adventure |

