.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-15::.
City: prague, nizza, liverpool, hamburg
There are 4 different nationalities: german, dutch, french, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the german is on the right of the french##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to prague is the russian##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to prague and the person driving the bike##2
7. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| City          | liverpool | prague    | hamburg | nizza |
| Nationality   | dutch  | russian    | french      | german     |
| Transport     | airplane | quad-bike | scooter   | bike      |

