.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-19::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, colonial, cottage
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, kale, kiwi, mango
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, may, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the farmhouse house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the farmhouse house and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| House      | farmhouse | cottage    | gothic-revival | colonial  |
| Food          | kale          | asparagus | mango       | kiwi      |
| Birthday   | may     | july    | november     | january |

