.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, mouse, guinea-pig
House: modern, cape-cod, cottage, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, skateboarding, surfing
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the modern house##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the mouse##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the cottage house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Pet    | mouse | lizard  | rat  | guinea-pig           |
| House     | modern | cottage | cape-cod   | futuristic |
| Sport   | surfing   | golf       | biathlon | skateboarding  |

 